      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FINS UP WENDY (4) unfancied latest but hit the ground running and gave a sight, holding on for a minor placing (20.22) at this track in a Grade 6 over 366m. Winning claims. BUGATTI ROGUE (1) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at Grafton over 450m behind Mr. Einstein (27.17) in a Mix. Can do much better this time. GOT HIM GOING (5) was an effortless winner two back scoring by half a length but could manage only midfield last time when finished 5th and beaten 5 lengths at Q Straight (16.85). Strong form has emerged from his last run. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. LUMINATE (2) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
